<br>
No more language barriers, no more TLC destroying all low-level NEW beastlord quests, etc.<br>
<br>
All the other problems with &quot;normal&quot; servers are also mostly absent.  Population is low like FV, you don't get all the /auction spam because there is no economy (like FV), and dewds seem surprisingly absent.<br>
<br>
Okay, there is a LOT of twinkage in evidence, but that's never really bothered me as long as the population is low enough to prevent everything from being farmed constantly.<br>
